           move      06                   to   v-car                  .
           move      02                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      i-ide-fas            to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
