           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      03                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      all   "="            to   v-alf                  .
