      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       acc-cod-ass-625.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione e visualizzazione della     *
      *                  * quantita' da esplodere in funzione del      *
      *                  * numero decimali quantita'                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rr-deq-ass           =    zero
                     divide   1000        into rr-qde-ass
                     multiply 1000        by   rr-qde-ass
           else if   rr-deq-ass           =    1
                     divide   100         into rr-qde-ass
                     multiply 100         by   rr-qde-ass
           else if   rr-deq-ass           =    2
                     divide   10          into rr-qde-ass
                     multiply 10          by   rr-qde-ass
           else if   rr-deq-ass           =    3
                     divide   1           into rr-qde-ass
                     multiply 1           by   rr-qde-ass
           else      divide   1000        into rr-qde-ass
                     multiply 1000        by   rr-qde-ass             .
           perform   vis-qde-ass-000      thru vis-qde-ass-999        .
       acc-cod-ass-800.
