                                          =    spaces
                             move  "S"    to   w-cnt-acc-ric-sel
                             go to acc-cod-ass-999
                     else    move  spaces to   w-cnt-tdo-ric-flg
                             go to acc-cod-ass-100.
       acc-cod-ass-999.
           exit.

